# Habit House PRD (Product Requirements Document)

## 1. Product Summary
Habit House is an AI-powered life operating system that automates habit building, daily planning, and personal growth.

Users do not manually track everything. The AI observes, predicts, and guides behavior.

---

## 2. Core Problem
Most habit apps fail because they require too much manual input and discipline.

Users forget, lose motivation, and stop using them.

---

## 3. Solution
An AI-first system that:
- Learns user routines
- Suggests daily actions automatically
- Reduces manual tracking
- Adapts in real time

---

## 4. Core Features (MVP)

### 4.1 AI Onboarding
- Ask user goals
- Ask schedule
- Ask habits they want
- Auto-build initial plan

### 4.2 Daily AI Plan
- One simple daily screen
- 3–7 recommended actions
- Auto-adjusted based on behavior

### 4.3 Habit Engine
- Create habits
- Track completion
- Auto-detect consistency patterns

### 4.4 AI Coach
- Daily feedback
- Motivation nudges
- Course correction

### 4.5 Weekly Review
- Performance summary
- Habit success rate
- Suggestions for next week

---

## 5. AI Behavior Rules
- Never overwhelm user
- Always suggest small steps
- Adapt difficulty automatically
- Prioritize consistency over intensity

---

## 6. Monetization
- Free tier: basic habits + tracking
- Premium tier: AI coaching + deep insights
- Future: affiliate + rewards ecosystem

---

## 7. Tech Stack (initial)
- FlutterFlow (mobile app)
- Firebase (backend)
- OpenAI API (AI engine)
- Firebase Analytics (tracking)

---

## 8. Long-Term Vision
Habit House becomes a personal AI operating system that manages health, productivity, learning, and goals automatically.
